DRAGUER
Do the best you--

[[PLOT POINT: Draguer finds out her genome is half Karamean]]

MANDELBROT
(interrupting)
Working...

There are a few seconds of silence as both wait for the result, Draguer anxiously, Mandelbrot with curious concern.

MANDELBROT
